Title: 业务用例
Describe: 你可以添加 `/` 来制作业务用例。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
业务用例

[Description]
None

[UML]
@startuml

(First usecase)/
(Another usecase)/ as (UC2)
usecase/ UC3
usecase/ (Last\nusecase) as UC4

@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
商业行为者

[Description]
None

[UML]
@startuml

:First Actor:/
:Another\nactor:/ as Man2
actor/ Woman3
actor/ :Last actor: as Person1

@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
